<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=3579">everquest.allakhazam.com/...?item=3579</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
Weighted Axe<br>
150 delay<br>
<br>
Would give nice clean test results.<br>
100% haste cap would be:<br>
150 * (1 / 2.0) = 75<br>
<br>
105% haste cap would be:<br>
150 * (1 / 2.05) = 73.17 ~ 73.1 <p><P>Milambus Mandragon<BR>
